<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>róng yào guī gěi sān yī shén 迦南1088</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 róng yào róng yào guī shén, guī gěi sān yī shén. yīn wèi tā xiàng xún qiú tā de rén cháng shī ēn.
 jiān nán zhōng tā fú chí, jué wàng zhōng tā zhǐ yǐn. róng yào guī gěi sān yī shén.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1088</hymn_number>
</song>